parameters.name: CustomLabels
parameters.description: The custom tags, which are used to filter tasks.

parameters.name: DatasetName
parameters.description: The name of the dataset. For more information, see [Create a dataset](~~478160~~).

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries per page. Value range: 0 to 100. Default value: 100.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token.

If the total number of clusters is greater than the value of MaxResults, you must specify this parameter. The next call to the operation returns results lexicographically after the NextToken parameter value.

>  The first time you call this operation in a query, set this parameter to null.

parameters.name: Order
parameters.description:
The sorting order. Valid values:

*   asc: ascending order.
*   desc: descending order. This is the default value.

parameters.name: ProjectName
parameters.description: The name of the project. For more information, see [CreateProject](~~478153~~).

parameters.name: Sort
parameters.description:
The sorting field.

*   CreateTime: the time when the clusters were created.
*   UpdateTime: the time when the clusters were updated. This is the default value.
